Class 35 03/11/2025

IP Assigning to NIC

Rhel7:
======
Step1: Add NIC to server 
Step2: Identify New NIC card with "ifconfg" command
	# ip addr
Step3: Assign IP temporary
	# ip addr add <IP ADDRESS/NETMASK VALUE> dev <NIC NAME>
	# ip addr
Step4: Perminantly add IP
	# cd /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts
	# cp ifcfg-ens33 ifcfg-ens39
	# vi ifcfg-ens39
	TYPE="Ethernet"
	PROXY_METHOD="none"
	BROWSER_ONLY="no"
	BOOTPROTO="none"
	DEFROUTE="yes"
	IPV4_FAILURE_FATAL="no"
	IPV6INIT="yes"
	IPV6_AUTOCONF="yes"
	IPV6_DEFROUTE="yes"
	IPV6_FAILURE_FATAL="no"
	IPV6_ADDR_GEN_MODE="stable-privacy"
	NAME="ens39"
	DEVICE="ens39"
	ONBOOT="yes"
	IPADDR="192.168.29.125"
	PREFIX="24"
	GATEWAY="192.168.29.1"
	IPV6_PRIVACY="no"
Step5: Reboot the server and check IP details
	# systemctl reboot
	# ip addr
